quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  45,1,"Haa, Miim. Yewtere fii sugu …óee kalfe yawtiino ka cortewol Al baqarah."
  45,2,"Jippagol Alqur'aana, ko immorde ka Allah, Foolu…óo Mo fooletake On, √ëee√±u…óo e tagu Mun e kattal Mun e toppitagol Mun."
  45,3,"Pellet, hino e kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, tinndinay…ói kattal e gootaagu Allah ngun, wonannde gom…óim…ìe …ìen. Tawde ko …ìen taskorta maandeeji …óin."
  45,4,"Hino e tagugol on ngol kadi, onon yim…ìe …ìen, immorde e to…ì…ìere maniiyu, refti huyre, refti he…ó…óere, e ngun tagu ngu Allah saaki ka leydi hino ruuga, ko maandeeji wonii e …óum fow, wonannde yim…ìe yananaa…ìe wonnde ko Allah woni tagu…óo On."
  45,5,"Wonii kadi e luutongol jemma e √±alorma ngol, e kon ko Allah jippiniri ka kammu, immorde e ndiyam, O wuurnitiri …óam leydi ndin, fewndo ndi yoorunoo ndi alaa pu…ói, e firlitagol keneeli …óin, yiltindira …ói senngo kala, tuma woo, fii nafa mon, ko maandeeji non, wonannde yim…ìe haqqiloo…ìe …ìen. ∆Åe dallinora …óum, e wootin…óingol Allah ngol, e wonnde Himo ha…ótani ummitingol, O ha…ótani huunde kala."
  45,6,"∆äin ko maandeeji e hujjaaji …ói Men janngirta e dow maa…óa, an Nulaa…óo, e hoore goonga. Si tawii …ìe gom…óinaali yewtere Allah e hujjaaji mun jippinaa…ói e Jeyaa…óo Makko on, haray ko yewtere honnde goo …ìe gom…óinoyta?"
  45,7,"Halkaare e lepte Allah woodanii kala …óuu…óu…óo fenaande e bakktuuji !"
  45,8,"On geddo hino nana Aayeeje Allah …óen ka Alqur'aana hino janngee e dow makko, refti o duumoo e geddi e keeferaaku makko, o townitanoo jokkugol goonga kan, wa si tawii o nanaano …óen Aayeeje janngaa…óe e dow makko. Awa an Nulaa…óo, humpitu on bone makko laakara, …óum le ko lepte muusu…óe hino habbitii mo ton."
  45,9,"Si go…ó…óum hewtii mo e Alqur'aana, o jogitora …óum jalnori makko. ∆Åen sifor…ìe ngol jalkitugol Alqur'aana, hino woodani lepte hoynooje, √ëalnde Darngal."
  45,10,"Jahannama hino yeeso ma…ì…ìe, habbitii …ìe laakara. Jawle …óe …ìe faggitinoo duncanoytaa…ìe huunde ka Allah, wanaa sanamuuji …ói …ìe jogitinoo rewetee…ói …óin gaanin Allah, woni ko duncanoyta …ìe. Hino woodani …ìe √ëalnde Darngal, lepte maw…óe."
  45,11,"Ndee deftere nde Men jippini e Nulaa…óo Amen on Muhammadu, ko …óowoore e goonga. ∆Åen yeddu…ìe non Aayeeje Joomi ma…ì…ìe …óen, hino woodani …ìe lepte bon…óe muusu…óe."
  45,12,"Ko Alla gooto O woni eeltan…óo mon- ono yim…ìe- maaya ngo ngam laa…óe ndiyam ndoga e hengo, haa …óa…ì…ìon e …ìural makko e nooneeji paggitaa…óe dagii…óe, mbela joo njetton neemaaji Alla e dow mon."
  45,13,"Alla mbo senaade woodani eeltanii mon denndaangal ko woni e kammuuji hono naange e lewru e koode, e ko woni e leydi hono caatli e le…ó…óe e montaanji eken, wonii e eeltude …óiin noon dallilaajim baawka Alla e ngootaagu Makko, wonande yim…ìe miijatoo…ìe kaawisaaji makko …ói …ìe teskoo…ói."